*) class and table
*) mapping -> Annotation or XML

#Annotaion

make a class (assume as entity(class representative(like monitor of class in school)
@Entity -> javax.persistence.Entity


//@Entity(name="student_details)
i can change the name of entity by like this

@Table :-> this annotation is used for the rename and change the details of the table
@Table(name="myStudent")



*) now go to the hibernate.cfg.xml(configuration file) and add one more property
<mapping class = "package.location" />

note
at starting we have to open session (factory.openSession())
then we can use getCurretnSession number of times


